  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Cleric Domain Power</strong><br/><br/><p>You can give a creature a vision of madness as a melee touch attack. Choose one of the following: attack rolls, saving throws, or skill checks. The target receives a bonus to the chosen rolls equal to 1/2 your cleric level (minimum +1) and a penalty to the other two types of rolls equal to 1/2 your cleric level (minimum -1). This effect fades after 3 rounds. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>",
